data.description: Absolutely Adorable! You will fall in love with this remodeled 2Br +Bonus Room, 2 bath, 2 car garage home on a quiet interior lot in the Beautiful Gated community of SUNBIRD!  This Updated home features Luxury vinyl wood floors, fresh paint, newer roof, newer AC unit, soaring ceilings, Inside laundry and and even new Faucets, Fixtures and Fans!  The Freshly Remodeled Kitchen boasts wood cabinets, newer appliances, tiled backsplash and beautiful granite countertops!  The large primary bedroom has a remodeled bath with a custom walk-in stone shower and dual vanities!  Walk out back to your own private desert oasis with a paver patio, a gazebo and cinder block walls for privacy!  All of this located in the Heart of Sunbird and close to Restaurants, Shopping, Freeways, and More!
